You can change the `axisLabel.formatter` in the `yAxis`

```js
                     formatter: function (value, index) {
                        if(value>=1000000){
                            return value/1000000 + "백만"
                        } else if(value>=1000){
                            return value/1000 + "천"
                        }
                        return value
                    }
```

